<text><body>
<lb n="1118c05" ed="T"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="1118c06" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="1118c07"/><cb:docNumber>No. 396</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="T" n="1118c08"/><cb:div type="jing"><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="001"/><cb:jhead><title>佛說法滅盡經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="T" n="1118c09"/>
<lb ed="T" n="1118c10"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="1118060">（（僧祐…錄））十三字＝（（僧祐錄失譯））五字【宋】【宮】，（（僧祐錄失譯人今附劉宋錄））十一字【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="1118060">（僧祐…錄）十三字【大】，僧祐錄失譯【宋】【宮】，僧祐錄失譯人今附劉宋錄【元】【明】</note><app cb:word-count="13" n="1118060"><lem wit="【大】">僧祐錄中失譯經人名今附宋錄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">僧祐錄失譯</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">僧祐錄失譯人今附劉宋錄</rdg></app></byline>
<lb ed="T" n="1118c11"/><p xml:id="pT12p1118c1101">聞如是：</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT12p1118c1104">一時佛在拘夷那竭國——如來三月當
<lb n="1118c12" ed="T"/>般涅槃——與諸比丘及諸菩薩。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1118c1212" rend="inline">無央數眾來詣
<lb ed="T" n="1118c13"/><note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1118061" place="foot text">佛所＝如來【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1118061">佛所【大】，如來【宮】</note><app n="1118061"><lem wit="【大】">佛所</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">如來</rdg></app>，稽首于<note n="1118062" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">地＋（眷屬圍遶渴仰聞法）【元】【明】</note><note n="1118062" type="mod" resp="CBETA">地【大】，地眷屬圍遶渴仰聞法【元】【明】</note><app n="1118062"><lem wit="【大】">地</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">地眷屬圍遶渴仰聞法</rdg></app>。世尊寂靜默無所說，光明
<lb n="1118c14" ed="T"/>不現。賢者阿難作禮白佛言：「<note n="1118063" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔世尊〕－【宋】【宮】</note><note n="1118063" type="mod" resp="CBETA">世尊【大】，〔－〕【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118063"><lem wit="【大】">世尊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>前後說
<lb n="1118c15" ed="T"/>法威光獨顯，今大眾會光更不現，何故如此？
<lb n="1118c16" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="1118064" place="foot text">其必有＝必有緣【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118064" type="mod" resp="CBETA">其必有【大】，必有緣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118064"><lem wit="【大】">其必有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">必有緣</rdg></app>故，願聞其意。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p1118c1609" rend="inline">佛默不應，如是至三。</p>
<lb n="1118c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT12p1118c1701">佛告阿難：「吾涅槃後法欲滅時，五逆濁世魔
<lb ed="T" n="1118c18"/>道興盛。魔作沙門壞亂吾道，著俗衣裳，樂好
<lb ed="T" n="1118c19"/>袈裟、五色之服；飲酒噉肉，殺生貪味；無有
<lb n="1118c20" ed="T"/>慈心，更相憎嫉。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1118c2007" rend="inline">「時有菩薩、辟支、羅漢，精進修
<pb n="1119a" xml:id="T12.0396.1119a" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="1119a01"/>德，一切敬待，人所宗向；教化平等，憐貧念老，
<lb ed="T" n="1119a02"/><note n="1119001" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">鞠＝救【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鞠【大】，救【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119001"><lem wit="【大】">鞠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">救</rdg></app>育窮厄；恒以經像令人奉事，作諸功德；志
<lb ed="T" n="1119a03"/>性<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="1119002" place="foot text">恩＝思【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="1119002">恩【大】，思【元】【明】</note><app n="1119002"><lem wit="【大】">恩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">思</rdg></app>善，不侵害人；<note place="foot text" n="1119003" type="orig" resp="Taisho">捐＝損【宋】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1119003">損【CB】【麗-CB】【宋】【宮】，捐【大】</note><app n="1119003"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">損<note type="cf1">K14n0520_p0056a17</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">捐</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">損</rdg></app>身濟物，不自惜己，忍
<lb ed="T" n="1119a04"/>辱仁和。設有是人，眾魔比丘咸共<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1119004" place="foot text">嫉＝疾【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1119004">嫉【大】，疾【宮】</note><app n="1119004"><lem wit="【大】">嫉</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">疾</rdg></app>之，誹謗
<lb n="1119a05" ed="T"/>揚惡，擯黜驅遣不令得住。自共於後不修道
<lb n="1119a06" ed="T"/>德，寺廟空荒，無復修理轉就毀壞；但貪財物，
<lb ed="T" n="1119a07"/>積聚不散，不作福德；販賣奴婢，耕田種植，焚
<lb n="1119a08" ed="T"/>燒山林，傷害眾生，無有慈心；奴為比丘，婢為
<lb ed="T" n="1119a09"/>比丘尼，無有道德，<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1119005" place="foot text">婬妷＝淫泆【三】【宮】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="1119005">婬妷【大】＊，淫泆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="1119005"><lem wit="【大】">婬妷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">淫泆</rdg></app>濁亂，男女不別，令道
<lb ed="T" n="1119a10"/>薄淡皆由斯輩。或避縣官依倚吾道，求作沙
<lb n="1119a11" ed="T"/>門，不修戒律；月半月盡<note n="1119006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雖＝假【宮】</note><note n="1119006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">雖【大】，假【宮】</note><app n="1119006"><lem wit="【大】">雖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">假</rdg></app>名<note place="foot text" n="1119007" resp="Taisho" type="orig">誦＝講【宋】【宮】</note><note n="1119007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誦【大】，講【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119007"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">講</rdg></app>戒，厭倦懈
<lb n="1119a12" ed="T"/>怠不欲聽聞，<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="1119008">〔抄略前後不肯盡說〕－【宋】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="1119008">抄略前後不肯盡說【大】，〔－〕【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119008"><lem wit="【大】">抄略前後不肯盡說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>；經不誦習，
<lb n="1119a13" ed="T"/>設有讀者不識字句，為強言是，不諮明者；貢
<lb n="1119a14" ed="T"/>高求名，虛顯雅步以為榮冀，望人供養。眾魔
<lb ed="T" n="1119a15"/>比丘命終之後，精神當墮無<note n="1119009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">擇＝澤【宋】</note><note n="1119009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">擇【大】，澤【宋】</note><app n="1119009"><lem wit="【大】">擇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">澤</rdg></app>地獄，五逆
<lb n="1119a16" ed="T"/>罪中餓鬼、畜生靡不經歷，恒河沙劫罪竟<note n="1119010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乃＝能【宋】【宮】</note><note n="1119010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃【大】，能【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119010"><lem wit="【大】">乃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">能</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="1119a17"/>出，生在邊國無三寶處。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1119a1710" rend="inline">「法欲滅時，女人精進，
<lb n="1119a18" ed="T"/>恒作<note place="foot text" n="1119011" resp="Taisho" type="orig">功＝福【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119011" type="mod" resp="CBETA">功【大】，福【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119011"><lem wit="【大】">功</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">福</rdg></app>德；男子懈慢，不用法語，眼見沙門如
<lb ed="T" n="1119a19"/>視糞土，無有信心。法將殄沒，登爾之時諸天
<lb n="1119a20" ed="T"/>泣淚。水旱不調、五穀不熟，<note n="1119012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔疫氣流行死亡者眾〕－【宋】【宮】</note><note n="1119012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">疫氣流行死亡者眾【大】，〔－〕【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119012"><lem wit="【大】">疫氣流行死亡者
<lb n="1119a21" ed="T"/>眾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。人民勤苦，縣官<note n="1119013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">計剋＝剋罰【元】【明】</note><note n="1119013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">計剋【大】，剋罰【元】【明】</note><app n="1119013"><lem wit="【大】">計剋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">剋罰</rdg></app>，不順道理，皆思樂
<lb ed="T" n="1119a22"/>亂。惡人轉多如海中沙，善者甚少若一若二。
<lb ed="T" n="1119a23"/>劫欲盡<note place="foot text" n="1119014" type="orig" resp="Taisho">故＝處【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1119014">故【大】，處【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119014"><lem wit="【大】">故</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">處</rdg></app>，日月轉<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="1119015" place="foot text">短＝促【元】【明】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="1119015">短【大】，促【元】【明】</note><app n="1119015"><lem wit="【大】">短</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">促</rdg></app>，人命轉<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1119016" place="foot text">促＝短【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="1119016">促【大】，短【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119016"><lem wit="【大】">促</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">短</rdg></app>，四十頭白，
<lb n="1119a24" ed="T"/>男子<app corresp="#1119005" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">婬妷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">淫泆</rdg></app>，精盡夭命，或壽六十。男子壽短，女
<lb ed="T" n="1119a25"/>人壽長七、<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="1119017" place="foot text">八＝十【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119017" type="mod" resp="CBETA">八【大】，十【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119017"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">十</rdg></app>、九十或至百歲。</p><p xml:id="pT12p1119a2512" rend="inline">「大水忽起卒至
<lb n="1119a26" ed="T"/>無期，世人不信故為有常。眾生、雜類<note place="foot text" n="1119018" resp="Taisho" type="orig">不問＝無有【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1119018">不問【大】，無有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119018"><lem wit="【大】">不問</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">無有</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="1119a27"/><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="1119019" place="foot text">豪＝高【宋】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="1119019">豪【大】，高【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119019"><lem wit="【大】">豪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">高</rdg></app>賤，沒溺<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="1119020">浮漂＝流飄【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">浮漂【大】，流飄【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119020"><lem wit="【大】">浮漂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">流飄</rdg></app>，魚鱉食噉。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT12p1119a2711">「<note place="foot text" n="1119021" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔時有〕－【宋】【宮】</note><note n="1119021" type="mod" resp="CBETA">時有【大】，〔－〕【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119021"><lem wit="【大】">時有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>菩薩、辟支、
<lb n="1119a28" ed="T"/>羅漢，眾魔驅逐不<note place="foot text" n="1119022" resp="Taisho" type="orig">預＝與【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">預【大】，與【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119022"><lem wit="【大】">預</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">與</rdg></app>眾會。三乘入山福德之
<lb n="1119a29" ed="T"/>地，恬<note place="foot text" n="1119023" resp="Taisho" type="orig">怕＝泊【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="1119023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怕【大】，泊【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1119023"><lem wit="【大】">怕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">泊</rdg></app>自守以為欣快，<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="1119024">〔壽命延長〕－【宋】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="1119024">壽命延長【大】，〔－〕【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119024"><lem wit="【大】">壽命延長</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。諸<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="1119025">天＝王【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119025" type="mod" resp="CBETA">天【大】，王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119025"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">王</rdg></app>衛
<pb n="1119b" xml:id="T12.0396.1119b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1119b01" ed="T"/>護，月光出世，得相遭值，共興<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="1119026">吾＝五【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="1119026">吾【大】，五【宮】</note><app n="1119026"><lem wit="【大】">吾</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">五</rdg></app>道五十二
<lb ed="T" n="1119b02"/>歲。《首楞嚴經》、《般舟三昧》先化滅去，十二部經
<lb ed="T" n="1119b03"/><note place="foot text" n="1119027" resp="Taisho" type="orig">尋＝尊【宋】【宮】</note><note n="1119027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尋【大】，尊【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119027"><lem wit="【大】">尋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">尊</rdg></app>後
<note type="orig" resp="Taisho" n="1119028" place="foot text">（（復滅…文字））十字＝（（化滅聖王去後））六字【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="1119028">（復滅…文字）十字【大】，化滅聖王去後【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119028" cb:word-count="10"><lem wit="【大】">復滅盡，不復現。不見文字</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">化滅聖王去後</rdg></app>，沙門袈裟
<lb n="1119b04" ed="T"/>自然變白。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT12p1119b0405">「吾法滅時，譬如油燈臨欲滅時，光
<lb ed="T" n="1119b05"/><note n="1119029" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">明更盛於是便滅＝更明盛【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" resp="CBETA" n="1119029">明更盛於是便滅【大】，更明盛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119029"><lem wit="【大】">明更盛，於是便滅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">更明盛</rdg></app>——吾法滅時亦如燈滅。自
<lb n="1119b06" ed="T"/>此之後，難可數說。如是<note place="foot text" n="1119030" resp="Taisho" type="orig">之＝又【宋】【宮】</note><note n="1119030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之【大】，又【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1119030"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">又</rdg></app>後數千萬歲，彌勒
<lb n="1119b07" ed="T"/>當下世間作佛。天下泰平，毒氣消除，雨潤和
<lb ed="T" n="1119b08"/>適，五穀滋茂，樹木長大，人長八丈，皆壽八萬
<lb ed="T" n="1119b09"/>四千歲，眾生得度不可稱計。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p1119b0912" rend="inline">賢者阿難作禮
<lb n="1119b10" ed="T"/>白佛：「當何名斯經？<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="1119031" place="foot text">〔云何奉持〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1119031" type="mod" resp="CBETA">云何奉持【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1119031"><lem wit="【大】">云何奉持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT12p1119b1012">佛言：「阿難！
<lb n="1119b11" ed="T"/>此經名為『法滅盡』。宣告一切，宜令分別，功德
<lb n="1119b12" ed="T"/>無量不可稱計。」</p><p xml:id="pT12p1119b1207" rend="inline">四部弟子聞經，悲慘惆悵，皆
<lb ed="T" n="1119b13"/>發無上聖真道意，悉為佛作禮而去。</p>
